name: European Union Of Wholesale with Eggs, Egg Products and Poultry and Game
membership: EUWEP is a member of CELCAA aisbl (European Liaison Committee for the Agricultural and Agri-food Trade)
memberOrga: The Members of EUWEP are the European Egg Packers and Traders Association, the European Egg Processors Association, and the European Poultry and Game Association.
goal: To represent the interests of the EU egg sector in discussions with EU institutions
interests: Agriculture and Rural Development, Environment, Food Safety, Trade
euInitiatives: International Trade (WTO and bilateral negotiations), Animal health and welfare, Marketing standards, Hygiene, zoonoses.
